This isn't a "OMFGPROWTFUHAX" Clue scroll base, it's just what I thought of out of thin air and YES, it works.

note: I am only posting this [u]here[/u] so if it's anywhere else, the poster fails.


[center][b]Difficulty: 0/10 C&P (or 10/10 if you're a retard.)
Time it takes?: 1 min?
Tested On: Project Fox (Czar) <or wL v3 as someone claims.

First, open the file which contains your eating. DeltaScape would use "Potions.JAVA". My server would use Client.JAVA

Now, where your food is declared, put this:
[CODE]			case 952: //Spade
				if (absX == 3012 && absY == 3373 && playerHasItemAmount(2677,1)) {
				addItem(405, 1);
				deleteItem(2677, getItemSlot(2677), 3);
				setAnimation(830);
				sendMessage("You begin to dig.");
				}
				if (absX == 3227 && absY == 3201 && playerHasItemAmount(2678,1)) {
				addItem(2679, 1);
				deleteItem(2678, getItemSlot(2678), 3);
				setAnimation(830);
				sendMessage("You begin to dig.");
				}
				break;[/CODE]

The above will make the spade dig treasure stated in the absX and absY and ONLY will it dig them items up on that exact spot with the required item.

Next, underneath you will need to put your Caskets in.

[CODE]			case 405:
				deleteItem(405, getItemSlot(405), 3);
				addItem(ITEMID, 1);
				addItem(ITEMID, 1);
				addItem(ITEMID, 1);
				sendMessage("*optional, I used this for declaring my clues by a name*");
				sendMessage("You found *Treasure here*");
				break;[/CODE]

That's your rewards.

Finally, you must add your interface.

[CODE]			case 2677: //lvl 1 clue
				showInterface(3023);
				sendQuest("Close Window", 3024);//Close Text
				sendQuest("@gre@LVL 1. Clue", 3026);//Line 1
				sendQuest("", 3027);//Line 2
				sendQuest("", 3028);//Line 3
				sendQuest("", 3029);//Line 4
				sendQuest("", 3030);//Line 5
				sendQuest("", 3031);//Line 6
				sendQuest("", 3032);//Line 7
				sendQuest("", 3033);//Line 8
				sendQuest("", 3034);//Line 9
				sendQuest("", 3035);//Line 10
				sendQuest("", 3036);//Line 11
				sendQuest("", 3037);//Line 12
				break;[/CODE][/b][/center]



